{"tid":2287351,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[利害啦我的國] 解放軍奪回中印邊境兩個山頭!!","createTime":"2020-11-15T16:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T13:25:10.000Z","uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ac88751246778f1f010085c80e8ddfe62edc41c1","tid":2287351,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:16:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3ltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=9563aaec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a> 東網   內地學者揭解放軍曾用微波武器 奪回中印邊境班公湖山頭<br />\n2020年11月15日 下午4:51<br />\n<br />\n中國人民大學國際關係學院副院長、美國問題專家金燦榮近日出席講座時表示，中國解放軍曾在中印邊境地區的班公湖南岸，動用微波武器攻擊印軍特種兵，並成功奪回被佔山頭。<br />\n<br />\n金燦榮上周三（11日）在講座中提到，印方在今年8月29日派出約1,500名「西藏特種兵」，突襲班公湖南岸兩座山頭。由於該處連接中方在班公湖兩岸的陣地，解放軍必須奪回，惟過程中不得開火。軍方遂將微波武器放置山頭下，令在山上駐紮的印軍部隊突感不適、嘔吐，被迫撤離。<br />\n<br />\n據印媒報道，印軍近日披露了當日遭疑似聲波、微波武器攻擊的細節：該特種部隊所有士兵，當晚均出現惡心嘔吐、無法入睡的症狀，多人精神崩潰，喪失作戰能力。印軍指揮官最終被決定放棄該處兩座山頭；士兵撤離高地後，症狀隨即消失。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201115/bkn-20201115143851361-1115_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201115%2Fbkn-20201115143851361-1115_00952_001.html&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3ltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=b505bf97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201115/bkn-20201115143851361-1115_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f7311db9a33124ba269b91697b7c642361838cfd","tid":2287351,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:17:00.000Z","msg":"我的國大勝!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5163625edbacd99deaf73d6a60df04a2f5a9a2de","tid":2287351,"uid":265628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"紅軍再現.唔洗用劍既 用微波武器就得啦"},{"pid":"8128c0dc2aa5426200b8ce988207c4bb6fb9a7e4","tid":2287351,"uid":98507,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T00:03:09.000Z","msg":"諗起神探伽利略<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有集又係用微波令人出現幻覺"},{"pid":"cc3fe4253ed1b7e2830aebbad2be7ed6efe6d864","tid":2287351,"uid":77968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T13:29:04.000Z","msg":"幾時可以奪回蒙古?<br />\n明明唐、元、清三朝，蒙古都屬於中國<br />\n幾時內蒙人可以同外蒙人團聚?"},{"pid":"040f245157190cb492c952fa7bdca7cdf6586172","tid":2287351,"uid":83228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T00:03:46.000Z","msg":"個啲係高原反應<br />\n你拎重野上去<br />\n99%一樣有<br />\n愈大隻 要愈多氧氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3564f83d294bb065cf55b6c50c60c9734ae85c1","tid":2287351,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T13:25:10.000Z","msg":"搶印度嘢都叫奪回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}